data.description: HUGE TERRACE off the living space in this 2br/2ba loft in famed Chess Lofts. Industrial finishes include soaring concrete ceilings, new vinyl plank flooring in living space and bedrooms, exposed brick and large double stacked windows. Open kitchen with breakfast bar, stainless appliances, granite counters and 42" cabinets. Fully enclosed primary suite with two closets, soaking tub and separate shower. Lofted second bedroom perfect for at-home office, gym or nursery (not enclosed). In-unit washer and dryer and garage parking included! Chess Lofts is adjacent to Prairie District Park complete with playground and dog park. Conveniently located in the historical Prairie District, minutes to the Loop, Museum Campus, Soldier Field, Wintrust Arena, McCormick Place and restaurants. Easily accessible to Lake Shore Drive, expressways and public transportation. Investor friendly!!
